block.translation:
Of old was the agewhen Ymir lived;

Sea nor cool wavesnor sand there were;

Earth had not been,nor heaven above,

But a yawning gap,and grass nowhere.

block.original:
Valþi Herfǫþrhringa ok men;

fekk spjǫll spakligok spǭ ganda.



sāk vitt ok vīttof verǫld hverja.

block.translation:
Necklaces had Iand rings from Heerfather,

Wise was my speechand my magic wisdom;



Widely I sawover all the worlds.

